## SQL Queries Practiced

### Create Database
```sql
CREATE DATABASE cyberlab;
```

### Create Table
```sql
CREATE TABLE students (
    id INT,
    name VARCHAR(50),
    course VARCHAR(50)
);
```

### Insert Data
```sql
INSERT INTO students VALUES
(1, 'Sreeja', 'Cyber Security'),
(2, 'Rahul', 'Networking');
```

### View Data
```sql
SELECT * FROM students;
```

### Filter Data
```sql
SELECT * FROM students
WHERE course='Cyber Security';
```

### Update Data
```sql
UPDATE students
SET course='SOC Analyst'
WHERE id=1;
```

### Delete Data
```sql
DELETE FROM students
WHERE id=2;
```

