## Bash Programs Practiced

### Hello Script
```bash
#!/bin/bash

echo "Welcome Sreeja"
```

### Variables
```bash
#!/bin/bash

name="Sreeja"

echo $name
```

### User Input
```bash
#!/bin/bash

echo "Enter Name:"
read name

echo "Welcome $name"
```

### Conditions
```bash
#!/bin/bash

num=10

if [ $num -gt 5 ]
then
    echo "Greater"
fi
```

